Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.93,0:00:15.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] My favorite food?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.10,0:00:18.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Strawberries... I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:21.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[WRITER] I see! You have\Ncute tastes, Miss Iona.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:22.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[MALE STAFF A] Hate to say\N"I told you so,"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.73,0:00:24.94,Main,,0,0,0,,but Akira's down\Nin the rankings again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:27.65,Main,,0,0,0,,On top of that, she's\Nbeen ditching work lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:29.57,Main,,0,0,0,,She's really not\Nworth it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.65,0:00:31.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[MALE STAFF B] Eh, her\Nstyle doesn't really match
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:34.53,Main,,0,0,0,,our magazine anyway.\NKinda "low-class," y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:35.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[MALE STAFF A] So\Nwhat should we do
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:38.33,Main,,0,0,0,,about the front page\Nmodel for the next issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:41.42,Main,,0,0,0,,What d'you think? Drop\NAkira and go with Yuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.50,0:00:43.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[WRITER] Well,\Nthat's just lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.54,0:00:46.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I wish they'd have their little\Nbusiness talk somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.34,0:00:47.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I like them\Nwith some milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.05,0:00:50.30,Main,,0,0,0,,And just a pinch of\Nsugar. Is that weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.38,0:00:52.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[WRITER] Huh? Oh, right,\Nstrawberries. Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.05,0:00:55.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I always take the\Nbackside of my fork.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:57.27,Main,,0,0,0,,And smash them to bits.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.44,0:01:06.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Just so we're clear,\NI'm gonna make you apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.94,0:01:08.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:41.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:45.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE'S MOTHER] My gosh!\NWhat happened, Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.66,0:02:48.08,Main,,0,0,0,,You're soaked\Nto the bone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:50.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Your friends didn't come\Nwith you? Did they go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:53.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:59.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, dry yourself\Noff before-- Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:09.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'm up\Nfirst! Aki-lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:12.07,Main,,0,0,0,,We're gonna school\Nthis scrub, Piriluk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:15.99,Main,,0,0,0,,And don't go easy on her\Njust 'cause she's a newb!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:17.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:18.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:20.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama... will fight to win this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:24.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:25.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA gasps excitedly]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:30.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll draw. Drop a card in the\NEner Zone, have Piriluk, Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:32.50,Main,,0,0,0,,And now, say hello to Sky Cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:34.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama. Let's Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:36.22,Main,,0,0,0,, I summon Kukri and Ponya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:39.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Tch! You gotta tell your\NLRIG to lay off the coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:42.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:44.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] It's weird.\NI've never felt like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:47.64,Main,,0,0,0,,But battling Akira\Nis awful. It's painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:49.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] It is painful, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:52.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:54.98,Main,,0,0,0,,What the hell? No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:57.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought she was\Nsupposed to be a newbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:04:00.53,Main,,0,0,0,,You are correct. Though\Nshe's new to the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:02.20,Main,,0,0,0,,she takes battle\Nquite seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:03.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:05.66,Main,,0,0,0,,This is talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:07.21,Main,,0,0,0,,She has a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:09.16,Main,,0,0,0,,You trying to tell\Nme something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.25,0:04:12.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't you turn around\Nand say it to my face? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:15.92,Main,,0,0,0,,You know what? Screw you,\NI don't even care anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.01,0:04:19.01,Main,,0,0,0,,You just keep your mouth shut\Nand do what I tell you, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:21.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's get this crap\Nover with quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:22.18,Main,,0,0,0,,ARTS!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:24.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Time for\NPeeping Analyze.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:25.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:27.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Awww. Poor Ru-ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:29.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Now I get to pick a card level,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:31.60,Main,,0,0,0,,then all the ones in\Nyour hand go bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.69,0:04:34.06,Main,,0,0,0,,And since you dumb rookies\Nlove to play by-the-book,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:36.69,Main,,0,0,0,,there's only one answer:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:38.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Level Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:39.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:41.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:42.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[PIRILUK] It would\Nseem you missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:46.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Arrgh! Who cares! I don't\Nneed you to tell me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:48.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't you do\Nsomething useful
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.25,0:04:50.96,Main,,0,0,0,,and figure out her\Nwish for me instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:52.75,Main,,0,0,0,,My wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:55.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!\NTry not to flip out
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:58.55,Main,,0,0,0,,and wet yourself when I see\Nyour dirty little secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:00.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry it up, Piriluk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:03.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I haven't had my dose of\Nbutt-hurt babies today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:04.76,Main,,0,0,0,,There's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:07.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's your deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:10.19,Main,,0,0,0,,You LRIGs can't like,\Nmalfunction, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:13.27,Main,,0,0,0,,She has...\Nno wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:21.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she's right. I admit it.\NI don't have a wish yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:23.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Hah! What?\NLemme get this straight:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:26.53,Main,,0,0,0,,You're battling as a Selector,\Nbut you have nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:29.50,Main,,0,0,0,,you wanna fight for?\NThat is, like, so messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:32.37,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you, a\Nsociopath or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:35.08,Main,,0,0,0,,All the Selectors are,\Nlike, do or die when it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:36.63,Main,,0,0,0,,comes to their wishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:39.00,Main,,0,0,0,,And you're just crapping all\Nover that so you can "have fun?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.09,0:05:41.13,Main,,0,0,0,,That is sick, yo. Sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:44.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] Participating as a\NSelector without having a wish
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:45.97,Main,,0,0,0,,is more than just wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:47.39,Main,,0,0,0,,It's blasphemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:49.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I don't\Ncare what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:50.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:53.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Just means I\Nhave nothing to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:55.40,Main,,0,0,0,,So you can't scare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:57.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Arc Aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:05:58.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.61,0:06:01.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:04.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:05.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[PIRILUK]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:07.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:12.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:15.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] What the hell\Nis wrong with you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:18.71,Main,,0,0,0,,You just said you\Ndon't have a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:20.46,Main,,0,0,0,,So tell me:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:24.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Why the hell are you trying\Nto stomp all over mine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:26.22,Main,,0,0,0,,No, that's not\Nwhy I did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:27.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I just- wanted you to--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:30.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Don't give me that crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:32.68,Main,,0,0,0,,You just wanted to see\Nme suffer, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.77,0:06:35.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, and I bet you enjoyed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:35.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:37.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:58.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[rain patters]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:07:03.13,Main,,0,0,0,,"Met with Ruko and Yuzuki.\NPlayed WIXOSS at the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:06.59,Main,,0,0,0,,On our way back, we\Nbought stuffed dumplings."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.68,0:07:09.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko and Yuzu--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:11.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps in pain]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:17.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:23.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:24.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:26.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:28.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE'S MOTHER] What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:30.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] The words\Nare disappearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:31.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE'S MOTHER] What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:32.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] My notes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:35.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Everything I wrote\Nis just fading away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:39.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know why!\NI can't remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:40.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE cries]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:43.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:45.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[MALE STAFF A]\NIs Akira late again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:48.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona. Have you heard from her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:50.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:51.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[MALE STAFF A]\NYou know what? Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:52.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't even care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:54.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[MALE STAFF B] Right? She's\Noff the cover for next issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:56.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Good. Riddance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:58.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Better yet, why don't we\Njust drop her for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:00.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[MALE STAFF B] Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:05.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[rain falls]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:07.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Iona...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:11.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:13.91,Main,,0,0,0,,You have the scent\Nof battle on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:16.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Or the stink of\Ndefeat, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:18.71,Main,,0,0,0,,That reminds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:21.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you remember that poor girl\Nwho battled Iona a while back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:25.25,Main,,0,0,0,,That was her second battle\Nand her second defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:27.21,Main,,0,0,0,,In other words, she\Nwas one loss away from
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:30.22,Main,,0,0,0,,bidding farewell to her wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:33.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Knowing that she was backed into\Na corner, you approached her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:36.10,Main,,0,0,0,,And you sweet-talked\Nher into another battle
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:38.48,Main,,0,0,0,,with a free win as bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:40.64,Main,,0,0,0,,And as she sat there,\Nstruggling to breathe,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.73,0:08:43.40,Main,,0,0,0,,suffering from the illness\Nthat ravaged her body,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:44.82,Main,,0,0,0,,you betrayed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:48.15,Main,,0,0,0,,You crushed a dying girl\Nfor your own gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.24,0:08:51.11,Main,,0,0,0,,It wasn't just her wish,\Nbut her very life
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:53.37,Main,,0,0,0,,that you snatched away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:54.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] What does\Nit matter to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:57.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I can run my battles however\Nthe hell I want, can't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:08:59.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Can't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:01.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH] Yes, you certainly can.\NThough I do have to question
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:05.46,Main,,0,0,0,,the effectiveness of your little\Nmethod, since you lost so badly
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:07.21,Main,,0,0,0,,to the next girl Iona beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:10.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH] That's why you stopped\Nfeeding off Iona's scraps,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:12.09,Main,,0,0,0,,isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.18,0:09:14.55,Main,,0,0,0,,And why you started picking on\Nthe rookie Selectors instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:15.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:18.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH] Tell me how that\Nworked out for you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:21.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] Yet another\Nloss. Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:26.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want your filthy\Nhands disgracing any more
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:27.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Selector battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.36,0:09:28.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:31.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH] Your wish is to see\NIona's life ruined, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:32.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:34.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH] I know you\Nwant to beat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:37.03,Main,,0,0,0,,So why don't you challenge\Nher to a battle already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:39.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Why do you avoid it\Nwhen she's right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:40.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:42.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I can battle however\Nthe hell I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:46.21,Main,,0,0,0,,And either way, when I get\Nmy wish you're going down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:47.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUKO] Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:48.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.71,0:09:50.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:52.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH] Oh! Looks like\NYuko's here for the shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:53.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:55.97,Main,,0,0,0,,But I thought me and Iona\Nwere doing the cover today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:59.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] You don't have\Na shoot today. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:00.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.68,0:10:03.02,Main,,0,0,0,,While you were so occupied\Nlooking for rookie Selectors
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:05.06,Main,,0,0,0,,to pick on, you seem\Nto have lost your
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:06.69,Main,,0,0,0,,coveted position as a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:07.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:09.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:12.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH] Aw, are you gonna cry?\NYou tried too hard to ruin
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:16.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona's career and\Nended up ruining your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:19.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] I don't want\Nto keep them waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:24.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] Goodbye, loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:27.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] I don't care about\Nmy career, or my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:29.96,Main,,0,0,0,,or anything, as long\Nas I can ruin yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.05,0:10:32.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll tear you apart!\NWith my own two hands
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:34.22,Main,,0,0,0,,if I have to, you bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:37.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:39.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH] Time to put\Nher out of her misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:46.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU] It doesn't seem\Nlike you have a fever...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:49.19,Main,,0,0,0,,But you're still\Nnot feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:52.69,Main,,0,0,0,,No... My head feels\Nlike it's gonna explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:54.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:56.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll call the school for\Nyou and tell them what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:59.41,Main,,0,0,0,,You just lay there and\Ntake it easy, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:06.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Now I'm making\NGrandma worry again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:07.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:10.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh, and I bet\Nyou enjoyed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:14.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Why do I like\Nbattles so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:17.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Why do I keep\Nwanting to have them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:19.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I know all the horrible\Nthings that'll happen
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:20.80,Main,,0,0,0,,if I continue playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:23.14,Main,,0,0,0,,But still... I can't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:25.77,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have to cry, Ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:27.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Y'know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:30.15,Main,,0,0,0,,It makes Tama so happy to\Nsee you have fun battling!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:33.11,Main,,0,0,0,,So don't be sad! We can\Nhave lots of battles and--!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:34.74,Main,,0,0,0,,No! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:36.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:41.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOY A] Hey, Kazuki. You aren't\Ntoo busy today, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:42.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOY B] Yeah, let's hang!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:43.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:45.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay! Sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.46,0:11:46.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOY A] Didn't think\Nyou'd say yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:47.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOY B] Cool. We can\Ngrab some grub.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:49.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] If you like curry,\NI know a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:51.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOY A] Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:53.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Can we talk for a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:11:57.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL A] Nothing personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:11:59.64,Main,,0,0,0,,But you and Kazuki\Nare kinda leaving
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:00.89,Main,,0,0,0,,a bad impression on people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:02.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:03.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL B] Like, the way\Nyou two always hang out
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:05.31,Main,,0,0,0,,is bordering on creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:07.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Jeez, could you\Nbe any more blunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:08.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, don't look so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:11.61,Main,,0,0,0,,We're not teasing, we're\Nactually really worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:12.98,Main,,0,0,0,,You're worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:14.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[HONOKA] We've been hearing\Nall those awful rumors
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:16.74,Main,,0,0,0,,about you two, so we came\Nto give you some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:20.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm stupid?\NWhat's it matter to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:22.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:25.33,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, fine, I'm\Nactually worried about Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:27.75,Main,,0,0,0,,You, I couldn't care less about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:29.79,Main,,0,0,0,,When I see you\Nstalking him all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:32.25,Main,,0,0,0,,It just makes me\Nfeel sorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:34.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL A] Yeah, it's awkward!\NMaybe you don't realize it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:36.72,Main,,0,0,0,,but Kazuki's actually\Na pretty popular guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:40.30,Main,,0,0,0,,But now there's all these\Nweird rumors because you--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.38,0:12:41.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Jeez, nice attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:44.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL B] Guess what they\Nsay about them is true. Ew.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:46.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[HONOKA] Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:52.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:53.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:54.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Don't talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.19,0:13:00.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] What's wrong with\Nthem? Everyone's so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:03.41,Main,,0,0,0,,They're the creepy ones, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:05.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOUNG GIRL] Howdy-dooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:10.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew it! You're a\NSelector, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:15.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Yay! I finally met one.\NI am the awesomest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.34,0:13:18.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Selectors are\Nso hard to find!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:20.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way,\Nmy name's Chiyori!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:24.51,Main,,0,0,0,,So can we have a battle\Nalready? Pretty pretty please?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:27.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen, kid. Here's\Na little secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:28.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI] Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:31.39,Main,,0,0,0,,If you lose three\NSelector battles...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:34.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Something unspeakably\Nterrible happens to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:36.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.36,0:13:41.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Duh, I already knew that! It's\Nall written down, right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:44.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? A novel? Of WIXOSS?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:46.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI] Yup! So yeah,\Nafter your third loss,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:49.45,Main,,0,0,0,,the magical WIXOSS Factors\Ninside your body go crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.54,0:13:52.37,Main,,0,0,0,,and blow up like a hot air\Nballoon, until "kaboom!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:54.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Guts flying everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:56.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Pretty scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:58.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, that's not--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:14:00.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI] That's why\NSelectors are so cool, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:03.30,Main,,0,0,0,,They put their lives on the\Nline to fight for their wishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.38,0:14:04.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:06.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[laughter]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:08.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.35,0:14:10.68,Main,,0,0,0,,My girl here's a little soft\Nin the head, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.77,0:14:12.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Eldora!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:15.52,Main,,0,0,0,,She'll see how hard my\Nhead is when we battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.61,0:14:18.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Now! Back to what I\Nwas saying before!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:21.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm offering my commemorative\Nfirst battle to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.57,0:14:24.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Ms. Selector-on-the-playground!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.45,0:14:25.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.57,0:14:28.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[HONOKA laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:30.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, stop it. You're\Ntoo much, Kazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.33,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not that\Nbig a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:33.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[HONOKA] You don't have\Nto go home yet, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:36.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Uh, no, I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:37.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[HONOKA] Oh good! There's\Nstill a bunch of stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:40.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I need to ask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:44.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI] C'mon, let's\Nbattle! Please! For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.68,0:14:45.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:48.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:49.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.89,0:14:54.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Yay! Finally!\NIt's battle time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:57.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[knock on door]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:01.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sweetie, I've\Ngotta step out for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:03.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Try to take it easy, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:10.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] It's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:12.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel like I've been\Nsearching for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.79,0:15:14.66,Main,,0,0,0,,But I can't remember\Nwhat it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:17.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[bird chirping]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:20.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] I just know\Nthat if I can't have it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:22.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing matters...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.09,0:15:25.01,Main,,0,0,0,,And there's no reason\Nto be alive anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:34.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:37.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI] The bitter,\Nbitter taste of defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:40.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA] Yep, she's strong.\NWay stronger than you, Chiyori.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:43.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that. Bet that was\Na waste of your time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:45.49,Main,,0,0,0,,You're so rude!\NLearn the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:48.78,Main,,0,0,0,,In her first fight the\Nheroine has to lose, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:51.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA] Yeah, I'll be sure\Nto write that one down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:54.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI] Oh! Here,\Ngive this a read, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:56.83,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll meet again\Nfor sure. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:58.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Fare thee well,\NSelector!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:15:59.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:01.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI makes engine noises]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:06.09,Main,,0,0,0,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:08.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Well, I finally won.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.43,0:16:10.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.43,0:16:11.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] All it takes\Nare three losses
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:13.97,Main,,0,0,0,,and my wish is gone forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:16.23,Main,,0,0,0,,But there's no telling how\Nmany times I have to win
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.31,0:16:20.19,Main,,0,0,0,,if I want it to come true.\NIsn't that the way it works?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:22.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] "Only when the\Nconditions are met."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:24.44,Main,,0,0,0,,"The conditions," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.53,0:16:26.99,Main,,0,0,0,,That's kind of cryptic,\Ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:30.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll tell me\Nafter it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:33.24,Main,,0,0,0,,All I've thought about is\Nwinning, but now I wonder
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.33,0:16:35.66,Main,,0,0,0,,what would happen if\Nmy wish was corrupted?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:40.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Maybe Kazuki would\Ndrift away from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:42.34,Main,,0,0,0,,No, it has to be\Nworse than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:44.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet he would end up hating\Nme and I'd never see him
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:47.30,Main,,0,0,0,,again for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:53.72,Main,,0,0,0,,He was with that girl.\NI wonder where they went?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:55.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:57.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe they went to Momoka's\Nplace to pick out cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.81,0:17:00.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I think his friends are\Nstill new to the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:03.15,Main,,0,0,0,,That used to be "our thing"\Nwe did together, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:04.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] Yuzuki, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:06.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Then maybe\Nthey'll go to a movie
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:08.24,Main,,0,0,0,,and stop by the\Nfood court afterwards
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:09.86,Main,,0,0,0,,to try out their new decks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:12.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Then they'll get a snack\Nand exchange numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:16.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Laugh and smile...\NWalk home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:18.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.54,0:17:21.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:23.38,Main,,0,0,0,,If they're going to\Ntake Kazuki away from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:26.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd rather just die now\Nand get it over with!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:31.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] No matter\Nhow upset you may be,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:33.43,Main,,0,0,0,,you should never say\Nsomething like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:37.31,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't think I'm serious?\NI hate you for lying to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:42.48,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I know, I know I need you\Nfor my wish to come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:44.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:46.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I know Akira made\Na fool of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:48.98,Main,,0,0,0,,but I did beat that\Nnew girl, no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.07,0:17:51.70,Main,,0,0,0,,If I still have a shot at\Nbecoming an Eternal Girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.78,0:17:56.24,Main,,0,0,0,,then my wish can come true!\NKazuki can be mine forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:18:00.04,Main,,0,0,0,,And he won't be\Ntaken away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:05.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] Listen. I am your\NLRIG, through thick and thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:10.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I will always follow you.\NWherever fate take us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.93,0:18:15.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] When I was\Nliving with Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:20.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think I asked for too\Nmuch. I wasn't spoiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:22.89,Main,,0,0,0,,She always wanted\Nto be left alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:26.69,Main,,0,0,0,,so I tried not to\Nbother her. But--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:28.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO'S MOTHER] I don't know\Nwhat Ruko's thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:31.90,Main,,0,0,0,,There's something...\Nscary about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:34.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I never knew how or\Nwhy I was scaring my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:38.37,Main,,0,0,0,,And that made me afraid, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:41.87,Main,,0,0,0,,But I'm fine as long as I have\NGrandma and Ayumu with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:44.33,Main,,0,0,0,,And I try not to ask for\Ntoo much from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:47.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to scare anyone,\Nor bother anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:18:51.26,Main,,0,0,0,,or hurt anyone ever\Nagain. But now--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.84,0:18:56.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Y'know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:58.76,Main,,0,0,0,,It makes Tama so happy to\Nsee you have fun battling!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:02.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:05.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] No! No, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:07.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.69,0:19:13.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Where do you get\Noff acting like a victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:15.49,Main,,0,0,0,,You just wanted\Nto see me suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:18.41,Main,,0,0,0,,And I bet you enjoyed\Nit, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:19.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.45,0:19:24.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU] Ru. Wake up, Ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:26.37,Main,,0,0,0,,There's a phone call for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:28.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I explained that\Nyou were asleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:31.25,Main,,0,0,0,,but apparently, it's\Nsomething important.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:32.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:46.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[door bell chimes]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.98,0:19:48.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE'S MOTHER] Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:52.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE'S MOTHER] Sorry to\Njust call out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you like parfaits?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.32,0:19:56.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I probably should've\Nasked before I ordered,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:57.86,Main,,0,0,0,,but I hope it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:19:59.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Uh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:01.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe usually gets the\Nkind with candied chestnuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:03.45,Main,,0,0,0,,This one looks awfully good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:06.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll have to come back\Nhere with her some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.50,0:20:07.92,Main,,0,0,0,,So what did you--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:11.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I looked through\NHitoe's phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.84,0:20:15.05,Main,,0,0,0,,She had your number and\NYuzuki's in her contacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:16.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:18.97,Main,,0,0,0,,You must think I'm a\Nhorrible mother for snooping,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:20.80,Main,,0,0,0,,but I also found this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.89,0:20:22.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.26,0:20:24.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on. Is this the notebook\Nshe kept on WIXOSS?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:26.18,Main,,0,0,0,,You've seen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.27,0:20:27.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:29.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE'S MOTHER] Hitoe\Ncan't read it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.69,0:20:32.48,Main,,0,0,0,,She said that all the\Nwords were "disappearing."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.57,0:20:35.03,Main,,0,0,0,,She also tells me she\Ndoesn't remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.11,0:20:36.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.91,0:20:42.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] Today, Ruko\Nand Yuzuki and I
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.99,0:20:44.87,Main,,0,0,0,,bought a matching\Nset of scrunchies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:46.50,Main,,0,0,0,,They both looked\Nreally cute
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.58,0:20:49.71,Main,,0,0,0,,when they put them in their\Nhair. They said I was cute too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:51.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll have to take\Ntheir word for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:54.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I was already so happy,\Nbut having the chance
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.67,0:20:56.05,Main,,0,0,0,,to be together with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:21:00.26,Main,,0,0,0,,sharing all of our fun and\Njoy, it was just wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:03.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Friendship truly is\Na beautiful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:06.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.93,0:21:08.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE'S MOTHER] She was so\Nhappy to make new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.93,0:21:10.73,Main,,0,0,0,,She wouldn't stop\Ntalking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:13.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know what went wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:15.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko, please, if there's\Nanything you can tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:17.36,Main,,0,0,0,,about what happened,\Neven if you had an argument
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:19.61,Main,,0,0,0,,or she got angry at you over\Nsomething, I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.70,0:21:22.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I promise I'm not trying to\Nblame you, but it seems like
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:26.16,Main,,0,0,0,,something just snapped and I\Nneed to know what caused it--!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:28.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.58,0:21:30.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko... Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:31.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:34.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Hitoe lost three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:35.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE'S MOTHER gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:39.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I was just having fun,\Nbattling with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.42,0:21:41.97,Main,,0,0,0,,We didn't know what\Nwould happen if we lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:44.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, her wish had\Nalready come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:47.64,Main,,0,0,0,,We didn't know it would\Nget corrupted like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.72,0:21:51.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko, I don't... Please, just\Nexplain what this is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.94,0:21:53.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.15,0:21:59.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I feel so lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.53,0:22:02.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Everything is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.57,0:22:05.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.66,0:22:07.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.00,0:23:41.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH] You came here because\Nyou wanted to battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.46,0:23:44.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Why are you\Nsaying this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.17,0:23:46.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] I want nothing\Nmore than to battle you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.84,0:23:47.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.93,0:23:50.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH] Forget it\Nand have some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.43,0:23:51.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.43,0:23:53.14,Main,,0,0,0,,The Girl's Desire.
